exports[`feature manifest formats human-readable report with fixed timestamp 1`] = `
"=== Todos Feature Manifest (local-only) ===
Schema: todos.feature_manifest.v1
Generated: 2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z
Active profile: minimal — Low-token MCP session bootstrap and task workflow

Summary:
  Feature areas: 6
  CLI commands:  162
  MCP tools:     325 (8 in active profile)
  Profiles:      6
  Env vars:      7

Feature areas:
  - Task workflow: Create, claim, start, complete, and fail tasks with agent coordination.
  - Agent coordination: Multi-agent leases, runs, heartbeats, and focus mode.
  - Projects and plans: Projects, task lists, plans, and bootstrap/discovery.
  - Import and export: Local bundles, todos.md sync, database backup, and artifacts.
  - Verification and security: Evidence, sandbox checks, secret scanning, and workspace trust.
  - Meta and discovery: CLI reference, parity reports, profiles, and capability manifests.

MCP tool groups:
  - Meta: 20 tools
  - Tasks: 162 tools
  - Projects and plans: 1 tools
  - Agents: 5 tools
  - Agent runs: 2 tools
  - Coordination: 17 tools
  - Graph and dependencies: 10 tools
  - Import and export: 29 tools
  - Operations: 8 tools
  - Security: 7 tools
  - Cloud bridge: 7 tools
  - Workflow utilities: 57 tools

Profiles:
  - read_only: Read tasks, projects, search — no mutations
  - agent_safe: Agent workflow: claim, start, complete, comment — no destructive ops
  - minimal: Low-token MCP session bootstrap and task workflow
  - standard: Default MCP/CLI minus admin/webhook/template tools
  - full: All local tools including templates and webhooks
  - admin: Full access including migrations and cloud bridge tools

Try:
  todos features list              # capability discovery summary
  todos features manifest --json   # full manifest
  TODOS_PROFILE=minimal todos-mcp  # low-token MCP session"
`;
